file.name: Address.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
Address:
  type: object
  description: The address object. It indicates the current URL and the referring URL.
  properties:
    url:
      type: string
      maxLength: 4096
      description: URL
    referringUrl:
      type: string
      maxLength: 4096
      description: referral URL
